<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
	<link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        /* Order Section */
        .order-section {
            margin: 30px 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative; /* Stays above the blurred background */
            z-index: 1;
            width: 90%; /* Default width */
            max-width: 500px; /* Limit width for larger screens */
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in width calculations */
        }

            .order-section p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                line-height: 1.5; /* Better readability */
            }

            .order-section a.order-now {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
                background-color: #ffdd57;
                color: #333;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

                .order-section a.order-now:hover {
                    background-color: #ffc107;
                    color: #222;
                    transform: scale(1.05); /* Add a slight zoom on hover */
                }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="welcome-screen"></div>
    <div class="order-section">
        <p>هذا الموقع مخصص لطلب البطاقات والدوسيات، بالإضافة إلى عرض تفاصيل العروض المتاحة.</p>
        <a class="order-now" asp-action="Shop" asp-controller="Home" style="text-decoration:none;">اطلب الآن</a>
    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
